{"tid":1407893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵站內派單程飛嘅同我入哂嚟","createTime":"2019-08-04T16:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T00:37:00.000Z","uid":196615,"like":143,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3e8dc51cab949dd9bf4c6d9d6767c839c362ad","tid":1407893,"uid":196615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"首先我好多謝你地咁有心出錢出力派飛送仔女返屋企<br />\n但係呢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">$15.5係基本盤呀你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n你話大西北打爆上到$40張張貴一倍就無得講(而其實有有心人已經開始派哥陣嗌埋大西北very good)<br />\n<br />\n你買得啲七個半十個半嘅飛，啲仔女個個發完夢攰到乜咁仲要出唔到閘，<br />\n我企閘頭見過唔止一次，佢地真係會好撚驚㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n又唔係個個識／知要補飛，又唔敢跳閘，<br />\n就咁企撚咗係個閘度，<br />\n仲要咁攰人地一問佢就爆哂邊度拎飛入閘㗎喇，<br />\n遇著我地同路人還好，遇著便衣狗咁點算？渣都無啦你老母<br />\n<br />\n再重申三次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">$15.5係基本盤呀你老味</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">$15.5係基本盤呀你老味</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">$15.5係基本盤呀你老味</span></span><br />\n<br />\n推哂俾你班負責課金嘅睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7965d8b66592567233536490d85e5372a1835af2","tid":1407893,"uid":286817,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:11:17.000Z","msg":"每次都買15.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr